            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, the reference book is getting pretty full. It's getting hard to find things in it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You have a hard time keeping things in order, after all. I'll teach you how to properly use a reference book."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Really? What should I do?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "You could do this, for example."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "If you do this, it will be much easier to use."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I think I can do this. Thank you, Plachta."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You can now Clip contents from the reference book."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Pressing <IM15> in the field allows you to quickly open Clipped entries."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You can add Clips by selecting \"Clip\" in the reference book submenu."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Would you like to view the explanation for Clips?"
